{"lemma":"زُعاقِ","slug":"زُعاقِ","root":"ز.ع.ق","root_slug":"ز-ع-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/ز-ع-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n17781","n17783"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B2%D9%8F%D8%B9%D8%A7%D9%82%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n17781","headword_ar":"زُعَاقٌ","root":"zEq","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A disposition to take fright and run away at random."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IF, O, K.) ―         -b2-  And hence, (IF, O,) as an epithet applied to a mountain-goat,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Wont to take fright and run away at random."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IF, O, K.)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Salt"},{"kind":"text","text":"water: (S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"very salt"},{"kind":"text","text":"water; like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuraAqN","text_ar":"حُرَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hrq","text_ar":"حرق"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or water"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is bitter,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mur~N galiyZN","text_ar":"مُرٌّ غَلِيظٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", Lth, O, K, both of which epithets, applied to water, signify the same, TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"glZ","text_ar":"غلظ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that it cannot be drunk"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, O, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by reason of its bitterness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"saltness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bitterness and saltness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"burning saltness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intense bitterness"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"saltness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, O:) used alike as sing. and pl. (TA.) ―         -b2-  One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^akalotuhu zuEaAqFA","text_ar":"اَكَلْتُهُ زُعَاقًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I ate it with so much salt in it that it was bitter."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, O.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mazoEuwqN","text_ar":"مَزْعُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["IF","O","S","Lth","K"]},{"entry_id":"n17783","headword_ar":"زَعَّاقٌ","root":"zEq","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One who drives away the beasts, and cries out after them."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaAEiqN","text_ar":"زَاعِقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  Applied to a horse,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A good goer;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strong to walk,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"go:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-' Abbád, K:) and also (Ibn- ' Abbád)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"very quick."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-' Abbád, K.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}